modules.description: This module decodes and encodes quoted-printable data as defined by RFC2047, specifically handling inline encoded text used in email headers. It processes byte sequences through incremental decoding and encoding operations, supporting non-blocking input and output with explicit buffer management. Concrete use cases include parsing and generating email headers that contain encoded non-ASCII text.

This module decodes and encodes quoted-printable data as defined by RFC2045, specifically handling email content encoding. It processes byte sequences through incremental decoding and encoding operations, supporting non-blocking input and output with explicit buffer management. Concrete use cases include parsing and generating email bodies that contain 8-bit character data while adhering to 7-bit transport constraints.
